## 🐛 Critical Fixes Applied (Last Session)

### 1. User Creation Fixed
- **Issue:** Database rejected user creation due to "Invalid parameter number" and missing required columns.
- **Resolution:**
  - Mapped all 50+ required columns from `gibbonPerson` schema.
  - Used unique named parameters (e.g., `:firstName`, `:preferredName`) to prevent PDO errors.
  - Added valid default values for all strict non-null columns.

### 2. Notification System Fixed
- **Issue:** Frontend crashed with "SyntaxError" and API returned 404.
- **Resolution:**
  - Implemented `/api/notifications` endpoints (GET list, POST mark-as-read).
  - Fixed syntax error in [NotificationBell.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/components/NotificationBell.tsx) (restored missing `try` block).
  - Corrected component scope issues in React (removed erroneous closing brace).

### 3. Gallery Video Support
- **Issue:** Video uploads were rejected or not displayed.
- **Resolution:**
  - Updated [ImageUploader.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/ImageUploader.php) to accept `.mp4`, `.webm`, `.mov`.
  - Increased upload size limit to 50MB.
  - Frontend now handles video files correctly.

### 4. Console Errors & API Fixes
- **Issue:** React warnings about duplicate keys and 404/401 errors for missing API endpoints.
- **Resolution:**
  - **Fixed Navbar:** Removed duplicate "Gallery" and "Contact" links causing React key warnings.
  - **Implemented APIs:** Added `/api/marquee`, `/api/admin/stats`, and `/api/admin/gallery/bulk-delete` to [api/index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php).
  - **Updated Frontend:** Modified [Marquee.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/components/Marquee.tsx), [ManageGallery.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/pages/admin/ManageGallery.tsx), and [AdminDashboard.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/pages/admin/AdminDashboard.tsx) to use correct, clean API routes.

