## 📝 Database Configuration (Next Step)

To enable login and data endpoints, configure the database:

### 1. Edit [/api/index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php) (lines 44-49)
```php
$dbConfig = [
    'host' => 'localhost',
    'name' => 'gibbon_ldm',    // Your database name
    'user' => 'root',           // Your MySQL user
    'pass' => 'your_password',  // Your MySQL password
];
```

### 2. Create & Import Database
```bash
# Create database
mysql -u root -p -e "CREATE DATABASE gibbon_ldm CHARACTER SET utf8mb4;"

# Import Gibbon schema
cd testbackend/core-31.0.00
mysql -u root -p gibbon_ldm < gibbon.sql

# OR import demo data
mysql -u root -p gibbon_ldm < gibbon_demo.sql
```

### 3. Fix MySQL Root Authentication (if needed)
If you get "Access denied for root@localhost":

```bash
sudo mysql
```
```sql
ALTER USER 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY 'your_password';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
EXIT;
```

